OL,6,F"It's been very difficult, because you
OL,7,Fknow I was here first but he's
OL,8,Fenormously famous."
OL,10,FThe mistaken bonus payslip was
OL,11,Fdiscovered while watching a friend in
OL,12,Fa play who was earning #300 a week for
OL,13,Ftheir performance.
OL,15,FHollander added: "I sat smugly in the
OL,16,Faudience having just done a BBC show
OL,17,Ffor #30,000 or something which was
OL,18,Fgoing to get me through the next year
OL,19,For so, and I was thinking 'Well,
OL,20,Fmarvellous, I'm very prosperous."
