OL,4,Cbonus mistakenly paid to Tom Hollander
OL,6,FAt the interval he discovered an email
OL,7,Fwith one labelled as "Box office bonus
OL,8,Ffor The Avengers".
OL,10,F"It was an astonishing amount of
OL,11,Fmoney," the 56-year-old told Meyers.
OL,12,F"It was not his salary. It was his
OL,13,Ffirst box office bonus. Not the whole
OL,14,Fbox office bonus, the first one. And
OL,15,Fit was more money than I'd ever
OL,16,F(seen). It was a seven-figure sum."
OL,18,F"My feeling of smugness disappeared,"
OL,19,Fhe added.
